ComicInfo.Summary:
In the introductory priced #0 issue, Dynamite introduces readers to an original 8-page story, overseen by co-writer and artist Frank Cho and infuses the issue with everything Cho fans want to see - beautiful women, thrilling adventures, and, of course, dinosaurs! Co-writer Doug (Red Sonja: QUEEN OF THE FROZEN, The 'Nam) Murray is along for the ride as is series artist Adriano (NBSG: ZAREK, Red Sonja) Batista as they bring the Jungle Girl to life! Featuring a cover by Cho, this issue #0 is a must-have and available for just 25 cents! Issue #0 leads directly into the first Dynamite Jungle Girl mini-series (and look for the ongoing Jungle Girl adventures in 2008!)
